                     <interp inst="t18280703-82-person580" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a porter of Gray's Inn. The prosecutor's wife gave me information, and I took the prisoner going through the square.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going through the square; the prosecutor's wife said, I had taken a pair of breeches; I said, she was mistaken, I would go anywhere to rectify the mistake.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 22.</p>
